::SnowCat::

She was near the entrance when she heard a bot call out.  She 
transformed into bot mode and stepped out into the door way.
She saw the bot standing there and extended her claws.  She wasn't 
sure who or what he was yet, but she was going to find out.
"What news do you bring?" She motioned with her hand for him not to 
come any closer.


--- In nbwrpg@egroups.com, "David Torrey" <Dachande85@m...> wrote:
> ::Eclipse::
> 
>     As he neared the main smell of the Maximals he picked up 
something else, he couldn't recognize it. (The Autobot smell, just so 
you know. He smells the Ark) Soon he saw a huge ship with a Maximal 
symbol on it. Sniffing around he smelled the Autoguns.
>     "Eclipse, Maximize." He said, because his comm systems didn't 
work in Beast Mode. "Attention all Maximals, I have news about 
Cybertron, a terrible action has occurred."
